== Months of Teichuu ==
In a {{ill|Common Era|ja|西暦|12=draft}} year whose final digit is 4 or 9 (i.e. when the Ten Heavenly Stems are {{ill|Jia|ja|甲|1=Kinoe (甲)|12=draft}} or {{ill|Ji|ja|己|1=Tsuchinoto (己)|12=draft}}), the month of {{ill|December|ja|12月|12=draft}} becomes the {{ill|Month (Calendar)|ja|月 (暦)|lt=Month|12=draft}} of Teichuu. However, the term “month” here may refer either to the month of the {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|12=draft}} or to a seasonal month (from {{ill|Minor Cold|ja|小寒|12=draft}} until the day before {{ill|Beginning of Spring|ja|立春|12=draft}}) as applicable.

== Days of Teichuu ==
The {{ill|Day Selection|ja|選日|1=Senjitsu|12=draft}} for a Teichuu day is as follows.
=== Day Selection ===
A Teichuu day is an intercalary day of {{ill|Hando|ja|犯土|12=draft}}.
