It is the 14th combination in the Sexagenary cycle; the preceding combination is {{ill|Bingzi|ja|丙子|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} and the following combination is {{ill|Wuyin|ja|戊寅|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}. In the system of {{ill|Yin-Yang and Wuxing Theory|ja|陰陽五行思想|lt=Yin-Yang Five Elements|lt_ja=陰陽五行|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, the {{ill|Heavenly Stems|lt=Ten Heavenly Stems|ja|十干|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}’ {{ill|Ding|ja|丁|1=Hinoto (丁)|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} represents yin {{ill|Fire|ja|火|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, while the {{ill|Twelve Earthly Branches|ja|十二支|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}’ {{ill|Ox|ja|丑|1=Ox (zodiac)|lt=Ox (丑)|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} represents yin {{ill|Earth|ja|土|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, and they interact by {{ill|Mutual Generation|ja|五行思想#相生（そうじょう）|lt=Mutual Generation|lt_ja=相生|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} (Fire generates Earth).

== Years of Teichuu ==
A year in the {{ill|Common Era|ja|西暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} that leaves a remainder of 17 when divided by 60 is a {{ill|Year|ja|年|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} of Teichuu.
