{{infobox Chinese|l=Yin Fire Ox|kanji=丁丑|romaji=hinoto ushi|onyomi=teichū|p=dīngchǒu|w=ting-ch'ou|mi=tʰiŋ⁵³ ʈʂʰoʊ̯²¹|y=deng1 chau2|j=deng1 chau2|ci=tɛŋ tsʰɐu̯|mc=tæŋ tʂʰjuw|oc-bs=tæŋ ʈʂʰuʔ|qq=}} ``` {{Sexagenary cycle comprehensive|qq=}} '''Yin Fire Ox also known as Teichuu''' (丁丑) (ひのとうし、ていかのうし、ていちゅう) is one of the [[:en:Sexagenary cycle|Sexagenary cycle]].
