ple|13=User:Immanuelle/2357|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2357 AD|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 24世紀}} * {{ill|2417 AD|ja|2417年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2417|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2417 AD|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} * {{ill|2477 AD|ja|2477年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2477|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2477 AD|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} * {{ill|2537 AD|ja|2537年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2537|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2537 AD|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} * {{ill|2597 AD|ja|2597年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2597|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2597 AD|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} * {{ill|2657 AD|ja|2657年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2657|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2657 AD|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} * {{ill|2717 AD|ja|2717年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2717|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2717 AD|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} * {{ill|2777 AD|ja|2777年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2777|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2777 AD|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} * {{ill|2837 AD|ja|2837年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2837|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2837 AD|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} * {{ill|2897 AD|ja|2897年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2897|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2897 AD|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} * {{ill|2957 AD|ja|2957年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2957|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2957 AD|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} |}
==Months of Yin Fire Ox== In a [[:en:Common Era|Common Era]] year whose final digit is 4 or 9 (i.e. when the Ten Heavenly Stems are {{ill|Jia|ja|甲|1=Kinoe (甲)|lt=Kinoe (甲)|2=ja|3=甲|4=zh|5=甲|1=Kinoe (甲)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Jia|13=User:Immanuelle/Kinoe (甲)|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Jia|13=User:Immanuelle/Kinoe (甲)|qq=}} or {{ill|Ji|ja|己|1=Tsuchinoto (己)|lt=Tsuchinoto (己)|2=ja|3=己|4=zh|5=己|1=Tsuchinoto (己)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ji|13=User:Immanuelle/Tsuchinoto (己)|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ji|13=User:Immanuelle/Tsuchinoto (己)|qq=}}), the month of [[:en:December|December]] becomes the [[:en:Month|Month]] of Teichuu. However, the term “month” here may refer either to the month of the {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=}} or to a seasonal month (from [[:en:Xiaohan|Minor Cold]] until the day before [[:en:Lichun|Risshun]]) as applicable.
==Days of Yin Fire Ox== The {{ill|Day Selection|ja|選日|1=Senjitsu|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Day Selection|13=User:Immanuelle/Senjitsu|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Day Selection|13=User:Immanuelle/Senjitsu|qq=}} for a Teichuu day is as follows. === Day Selection === A Teichuu day is an intercalary day of {{ill|Hando|ja|犯土|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Hando|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Hando|qq=}}. == See Also == * {{prefix|qq=}} * {{intitle|qq=}}
